      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in pristine, unmodified condition. This specimen features the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, utilizing its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and factory-spec wastegate actuators. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission, feeding power through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, with all original VIN tags present on body panels and no signs of oxidation on the subframe or suspension pick-up points. The double-wishbone suspension retains its OEM damping characteristics and rubber bushings, providing a tight, communicative steering rack response. Mechanically, the engine demonstrates exceptional health with uniform compression across all cylinders and a leak-down test within factory tolerances. This is an unmolested, collector-quality example for the discerning enthusiast who values mechanical purity and original engineering.",
